sculptor":0,"boardgameeditor":0,"boardgamewriter":0,"boardgameinsertdesigner":0,"boardgamehonor":1,"boardgamecategory":4,"boardgamemechanic":8,"boardgameexpansion":1,"boardgameversion":9,"expandsboardgame":0,"boardgameintegration":0,"contains":0,"containedin":0,"reimplementation":0,"reimplements":0,"boardgamefamily":13,"videogamebg":0,"boardgamesubdomain":1,"boardgameaccessory":0,"cardset":1},"secondarynamescount":0,"alternatenamescount":2,"primaryname":{"nameid":"779580","name":"Sylvion","sortindex":"1","primaryname":"1","translit":"Sylvion"},"alternatenames":[{"nameid":"2235932","name":"シルヴィオン"},{"nameid":"2475461","name":"실비온"}],"description":"<p>The mad Fire Elemental lord is out to burn down the dream forest. Attacking in waves using Fire Elementals, your only defense are trees and fountains and those animals brave enough to offer aid before scurrying away to safety. Using a unique drafting system and combining it with a tower defense game, will you be able to keep your forest green?</p>\n\n<p><em><strong>Sylvion</strong></em> is a tower-defense type game in which attacks come down four rows and in waves. You build a deck using a unique drafting process and play cards from your hand by paying with other cards in your hand. You can play cards to the rows like fountains and trees or play animals for instant effects or to manipulate the enemy decks of cards. When all the waves have finished, you must have kept the heart of the Sylvion verdant, or else the whole forest of the Oniverse will be destroyed.</p>\n\n<p>This game can be played in an introductory style, advanced mode, and includes two expansions and an appendix for further challenges and complexity.</p>\n\n","wiki":"<p><strong><a class=\"\" href=\"/wiki/page/Microbadges#\">Microbadges</a></strong></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/microbadge/42054\"><img alt='Microbadge: Sylvion - The Ravage' onmouseover=\"return overlib('Sylvion - The Ravage', WRAP );\" onmouseout=\"return nd();\" title=''class='mbimg'loading=\"lazy\"src=\"https://cf.geekdo-static.com/mbs/mb_42054_0.png\"></a> <a href=\"/microbadge/42054\">Sylvion - The Ravage</a><br />\n<a href=\"/microbadge/31300\"><img alt='Microbadge: Sylvion fan' onmouseover=\"return overlib('Sylvion fan', WRAP );\" onmouseout=\"return nd();\" title=''class='mbimg'loading=\"lazy\"src=\"https://cf.geekdo-static.com/mbs/mb_31300_0.png\"></a> - <em>Sylvion</em> fan<br />\n<a href=\"/microbadge/39457\"><img alt='Microbadge: Oniverse fan' onmouseover=\"return overlib('Oniverse fan', WRAP );\" onmouseout=\"return nd();\" title=''class='mbimg'loading=\"lazy\"src=\"https://cf.geekdo-static.com/mbs/mb_39457_0.png\"></a> - Oniverse fan</p>\n\n<p><strong><a class=\"\" href=\"/wiki/page/Components#\">Components</a></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n    <li> 64 Sylvan cards<ul>\n        <li> 16 Fountain cards<ul>\n            <li> 4x strength 1</li>\n            <li> 4x strength 2</li>\n            <li> 4x strength 3</li>\n            <li> 4x strength 4</li>\n        </ul></li>\n        <li> 16 Tree cards<ul>\n            <li> 4x vitality 1</li>\n            <li> 4x vitality 2</li>\n            <li> 4x vitality 3</li>\n            <li> 4x vitality 4</li>\n        </ul></li>\n        <li> 32 Animal cards<ul>\n            <li> 4x 8 different animals</li>\n        </ul></li>\n    </ul></li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n    <li> 64 Ravage Cards<ul>\n        <li> 32 Elemental cards<ul>\n            <li> 8x strength 0</li>\n            <li> 8x strength 1</li>\n            <li> 8x strength 2</li>\n            <li> 8x strength 3</li>\n        </ul></li>\n        <li> 32 Support cards<ul>\n            <li> 8x Blaze cards</li>\n            <li> 8x Simoon cards</li>\n            <li> 8x Desiccation cards</li>\n            <li> 8x Demobilization cards</li>\n        </ul></li>\n    </ul></li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n    <li> 16 Blazing elemental cards<ul><ul>\n            <li> 6x strength-2</li>\n            <li> 10x strength-3</li>\n            <li> and on the back of all cards: 16x strength-4</li>\n        </ul></li>\n    </ul></li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n    <li> 12 Edge cards (bloom side and desolated side)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n    <li> 32 Expansion cards<ul>\n        <li> Expansion 1 cards<ul>\n            <li> 8 Betrayal cards</li>\n            <li> 8 Extraordinary Feat cards</li>\n        </ul></li>\n        <li> Expansion 2 cards<ul>\n            <li> 16 Element cards : 4 Geyser, 4 Stone Rain, 4 Acid Lake, 4 Temporal Tornado</li>\n        </ul></li>\n    </ul></li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n    <li> 1 Ravage token</li>\n</ul>\n\n","website":{"url":"https://inpatience.com/en/Our_Games-8-SYLVION","title":"Game Page - inPatience"},"imageid":"6863747","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/LRuwX_qAGXDSWRF2fufzAw__small/img/zN5w-EtX4DTGPoYsqwqXquGUIs0=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic6863747.jpg","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/LRuwX_qAGXDSWRF2fufzAw__micro/img/oWnSAbd3pAUTA5o_MPr5M4548KU=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic6863747.jpg","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/LRuwX_qAGXDSWRF2fufzAw__square/img/pymc5C-TfCFW2Zt1yuoOq3rwyX0=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic6863747.jpg","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/LRuwX_qAGXDSWRF2fufzAw__tallthumb/img/nZLm7gspz_lhp_2-S8858rr-l3c=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic6863747.jpg","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/LRuwX_qAGXDSWRF2fufzAw__previewthumb/img/xdHnAhWGp3fCUXaso_ykSvlgGF0=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic6863747.jpg","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/LRuwX_qAGXDSWRF2fufzAw__square200/img/fCIWgdvw5C97sxD0gg7Uu_D01AE=/200x200/filters:strip_icc()/pic6863747.jpg","original":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/LRuwX_qAGXDSWRF2fufzAw__original/img/meUZVk9bubquyT4w47HZiULAcWg=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic6863747.jpg"},"imagepagehref":"/image/6863747/sylvion","imageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/LRuwX_qAGXDSWRF2fufzAw__itemrep/img/SCAoZc7EKy3TO3-ytMCrvYVhTys=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic6863747.jpg","topimageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/mGsp87E6qPXKcHdB42Fq